Mayonaka no lady, hitogomi ni magire

4
00:00:35,335 --> 00:00:41,399
Utsurigi na steppin' kurikaeshite iru

5
00:00:41,541 --> 00:00:46,379
Tsuyogari no face, tough na furi de

6
00:00:46,379 --> 00:00:48,711
Odori akashite mo

7
